Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.50,0:02:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(恐怖的毕克．萨姆！)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.66,0:02:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受不了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.83,0:02:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我所做的事\N竟同时一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.93,0:02:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,G战机，史中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.63,0:02:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回舰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.67,0:02:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左右引击，受损了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.93,0:02:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史中尉，听到吗？\N回答吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.27,0:02:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到了，在第三甲板降落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.07,0:02:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么事？少尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.61,0:02:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.18,0:02:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,右方的导弹很薄弱\N不要大意！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.02,0:02:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙劳‧波\N交由副舰长来做吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.49,0:02:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莱少尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.16,0:03:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽战斗中是禁止私人交谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.07,0:03:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但很见外呀！米莱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.30,0:03:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是去保护你\N我也是可做到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.80,0:03:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布莱特！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.81,0:03:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白你的感受\N在等你呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.64,0:03:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.81,0:03:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莱有点不适\N去代她一会吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.08,0:03:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来代替了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.65,0:03:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布莱特！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.35,0:03:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对空机关枪\N左方快接近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.82,0:03:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.36,0:03:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点！快点修好左右引击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.80,0:03:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏威多！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.27,0:03:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我修好被损的部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.27,0:03:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有加大二号引击的输出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.37,0:03:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加大点吧！\NOK，会做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.04,0:03:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有燃料和弹药的补给\N快点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.18,0:03:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请等15分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.05,0:03:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,10分钟\N我也去补给燃料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.95,0:03:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点吧！\N用10分钟去完成吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.95,0:04:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏威多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.19,0:04:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史中尉在那里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.86,0:04:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去了待机室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.49,0:04:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？谢谢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.38,0:04:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中尉，没受伤的呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.65,0:04:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少尉，来这里做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.83,0:04:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少尉，停止吧！\N很难为情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.94,0:04:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史中尉，出发准备完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.34,0:04:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立即来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.14,0:04:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜拜呢！         中尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.12,0:05:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请不要死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.96,0:05:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莱少尉\N虽人在年青时会有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.63,0:05:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不同的事\N但现在自己的感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.06,0:05:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要太过认真比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.97,0:05:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.84,0:05:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了吧！         中尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.44,0:05:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是能接受\N少尉的爱的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.25,0:05:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史中尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.78,0:05:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对于我来说\N少尉太耀眼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.69,0:05:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不同的世界   但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.82,0:05:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是便宜的东西\N妈妈的遗物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.79,0:05:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如失去就麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.96,0:05:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我好好保管吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.94,0:05:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.65,0:06:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那戒指拜托了，少尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.64,0:06:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.51,0:06:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月球背后\N南方的300公里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.05,0:06:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是基斯比加基地\N古兰拿达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.18,0:06:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所罗门要出击的军队\N不断在准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.82,0:06:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在马古比司令的麾下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.49,0:06:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,编成了一支舰队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.81,0:07:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.05,0:07:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在基地之内\N留下很多的战力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.12,0:07:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.99,0:07:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,注意吧！\N是新型的敌人呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.19,0:08:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？有多少台？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.13,0:08:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等，好像\N只得一台新型敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.40,0:08:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,余下只有多姆和萨克\N去攻吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.87,0:08:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等！对方的作战能力...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.51,0:08:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了呀！蠢材们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.44,0:08:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给他们看这毕克．萨姆和普通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.05,0:08:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MS不同之处吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.07,0:08:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如出来的话\N就快点出来呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.54,0:08:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷射枪竟然...\N怪...怪物呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.38,0:08:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怪物？去查个明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.65,0:09:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是基斯，阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.32,0:09:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？\N阁下在那里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.53,0:09:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在操控着毕克．萨姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.43,0:09:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对抗侵入的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.00,0:09:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，残余的舰队\N也出发了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.00,0:09:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用阁下亲自出击...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.67,0:09:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太天真了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.87,0:09:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用全部的战力\N去攻击不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.67,0:09:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茜拿，美利巴\N无事的逃出了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.20,0:09:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我军的逃生火箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.97,0:09:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路程是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.11,0:09:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想是从\N所罗门发射出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.18,0:09:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掩护的回收吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.78,0:10:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泰沙，所罗门的战斗\N好像是严重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.52,0:10:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用管那逃生火箭...\N失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.22,0:10:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请马古比殿下\N你明白兵士的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.82,0:10:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我！         这样的情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.46,0:10:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要相信的去救出同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.56,0:10:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兵士也一样\N和我们在宇宙中战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.16,0:10:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快点的话\N会离开回收范围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.80,0:10:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了，回收吧！      系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.96,0:10:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美利巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.29,0:10:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是同伴的舰队呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得救了呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.99,0:11:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽这家伙强大火力是好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.33,0:11:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但不可再使基地受到损伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基斯！         系，阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.33,0:11:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舰艇还余下多少台？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.00,0:11:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了敌方的新兵器和MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.57,0:11:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四分之三被破坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.17,0:11:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,余下是不能开动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.94,0:11:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！去突破\N敌方的中央舰队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.18,0:11:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也用余下的多姆和萨克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.48,0:11:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离开所罗门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.62,0:11:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阁下也请努力！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.62,0:11:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.27,0:12:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在后方，确认敌舰在移动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.81,0:12:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还可忍耐吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.34,0:12:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是在所罗门余下的敌军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.61,0:12:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也出发了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.84,0:12:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用反射镜系统\N能消灭他们吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.28,0:12:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如有60%\N的准确率的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.95,0:12:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去试试看吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.12,0:12:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,定向坐标是0635
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.80,0:13:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进入Y射线\N004，002
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.54,0:13:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在发射太阳能系统后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.80,0:13:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各舰队去消灭敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.34,0:13:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进入最大速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.41,0:13:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,错过去也可以\N还有在前方前来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.11,0:13:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一只也要击下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.26,0:13:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这边吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.60,0:13:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很拿手吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.04,0:13:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迟了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.51,0:13:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟是什么MS\N造成这样的破坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.38,0:13:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那边吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.13,0:14:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.31,0:14:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.16,0:14:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所罗门还在出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.32,0:14:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反射镜在瞄准
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.83,0:14:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？反射镜还在吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.51,0:14:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,余下的舰只\N去袭击敌方舰队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.84,0:15:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！         毕克．萨姆的目标是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.15,0:15:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞄准后方的部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.05,0:15:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要理会小卒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.32,0:15:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉中了弹\N在第三甲板回收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.69,0:15:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.39,0:15:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各部门\N去追着所罗门出发的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.96,0:15:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大型MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.43,0:15:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莱！   对不起中尉\N已没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.37,0:15:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！巴马士，回到副桥舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.98,0:15:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,转向180度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.98,0:15:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点，米莱！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.62,0:15:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是敌舰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.65,0:15:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧\N用全部雷射光射去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.79,0:15:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然，不只是大型的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.66,0:15:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在，的确弹回了雷射光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.30,0:15:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是用导弹才有效吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.00,0:16:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样下去，只有增加损伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.01,0:16:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毕克．萨姆单独去敌方舰队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.61,0:16:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之前\N发出逃走的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.28,0:16:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.38,0:16:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用了太多的战力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.69,0:16:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽很遗憾\N但只有放弃所罗门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.72,0:16:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那操控系统\N移到我这处吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.43,0:16:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们也各自逃走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.06,0:16:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，阁下！\N不要白白牺牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.06,0:16:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有多姆和萨克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.53,0:16:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如用那的话\N能从战场中逃去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.64,0:16:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！发出起航信号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.84,0:16:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毕克．萨姆由我来操控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.65,0:16:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样，所罗门\N会简单的击下吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.46,0:16:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.33,0:17:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样做很困难的吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.67,0:17:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要小看呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.01,0:17:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这毕克．萨姆是不怕雷射光攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.11,0:17:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等我带你们\N到地狱下去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.36,0:17:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巨大的MS\N在发射强力的磁场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.36,0:17:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是导弹，用导弹来迎击！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.81,0:17:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,压倒性的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.45,0:17:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到吗？\N如毕克．萨姆能量产生后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.55,0:17:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能一瞬间的\N打败联邦军呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.53,0:18:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史中尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.00,0:18:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相接后，用G装甲来吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.35,0:18:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真慢，阿姆罗少曹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.02,0:18:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是中尉，是打算怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.68,0:18:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有什么打算吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.49,0:18:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要破坏磁场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.16,0:18:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有接近去用雷射光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.66,0:18:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如这边的雷射光用完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.79,0:18:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用钢弹的雷射枪和雷射剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.80,0:18:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如用尽所有武器\N我会被打败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.83,0:18:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史中尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.43,0:18:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,私情是禁忌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.97,0:18:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.04,0:18:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可再更加的受损伤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.97,0:18:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽很悲伤\N但这是战争呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.41,0:18:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗！从下方去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.16,0:19:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下方吗？对空型态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.84,0:19:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还未行吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.51,0:19:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.28,0:19:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.20,0:19:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟被一台MS...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.67,0:19:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这毕克．萨姆被打败了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.21,0:20:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会被打败呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.31,0:20:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会被你打败呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.68,0:20:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会被打败！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.06,0:20:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吉翁的光荣，我的自尊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.20,0:20:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会被打败，不会被打败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.86,0:20:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会被打败呀！\N是什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.84,0:20:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.88,0:21:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所罗门...堕下了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.89,0:21:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样？泰沙\N用这古亚知送邵娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.19,0:21:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去古兰拿达吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.12,0:21:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我移到去知比\N去看清今后的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.83,0:21:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联邦军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.20,0:21:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那全部终于也失败了\N是吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.47,0:21:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你始终是坚持\N所罗门的作战参谋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.51,0:21:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还余下情报收集\N和逃生的兵士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.94,0:21:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以了\N我去执行那任务吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.32,0:21:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说谎的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.83,0:21:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能说是说谎吗？阿姆罗

